====Definitions====
{{head|zh|hanzi}}

# {{lb|zh|literary}} to [[say]]; to [[speak]] (used when quoting from a source)
# {{non-gloss|A particle.}}
# {{surname|zh}}:
## originated from {{zh-l|妘}}
## originated from [[Zhou]] dynasty feudal state of {{zh-l|䢵}}
## originated from surname {{zh-l|牒云}}
## simplified from {{zh-l|*雲}}
# {{lb|zh|Quanzhou Hokkien|Xiamen Hokkien|&|Philippine Hokkien}} to [[go]] on a [[pleasure]] [[trip]]; to [[roam]] around; to [[stroll]]; to [[saunter]]; to [[go]] for a [[walk]]
# {{zh-div|母}} {{lb|zh|Chinese linguistics}} the [[Middle Chinese]] [[initial]] of {{ltc-l|云}}, equivalent to the 3rd {{zh-m|等}} of the initial {{ltc-l|喻}}

